      "date": "2012-12-17 03:58:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a0053ffe-47fa-11e2-876e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
