          "email": "artem_blagodarenko@xyratex.com",
          "date": "2012-12-14 10:47:49.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2487 client: change resource locks type to rwlock",
        "message": "LU-2487 client: change resource locks type to rwlock\n\nClient deadlock between ll_md_blocking_ast, sys_close, and\nsys_open is possible. There are tree pairs of locks\nresource,inode; dentry,resource and inode,dentry. The deadlock\nis possible in systems that don't use dcache_lock.\n\nThis patch changes resource lock type to rwlock so two\nresource locks, can't lock because acquired for reading.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-675\nReviewed-by: Alexander Zarochentsev <Alexander_Zarochentsev@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Iurii Golovach <Iurii_Golovach@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Artem Blagodarenko <artem_blagodarenko@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I8ff42952457b4ece30a19c32cd15c67a49631cb4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
